            "id": "http://yoursite.com/2020/06/07/Fiddle-%E7%88%AC%E8%99%AB%E5%88%A9%E5%99%A8/",
            "url": "http://yoursite.com/2020/06/07/Fiddle-%E7%88%AC%E8%99%AB%E5%88%A9%E5%99%A8/",
            "title": "Fiddle--爬虫利器",
            "date_published": "2020-06-07T13:55:11.000Z",
            "content_html": "<h2 id=\"fiddle\"><a href=\"#fiddle\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"fiddle\"></a>fiddle</h2><p> Fiddler是一个http调试代理，它能够记录所有的你电脑和互联网之间的http通讯，Fiddler 可以也可以让你检查所有的http通讯，设置断点，以及Fiddle 所有的“进出”的数据（指cookie,html,js,css等文件，这些都可以让你胡乱修改的意思）。 Fiddler 要比其他的网络调试器要更加简单，因为它仅仅暴露http通讯还有提供一个用户友好的格式。</p>\n<p>Fiddler是最强大最好用的Web调试工具之一，它能记录所有客户端和服务器的http和https请求，允许你监视，设置断点，甚至修改输入输出数据，Fiddler包含了一个强大的基于事件脚本的子系统，并且能使用.net语言进行扩展。你对HTTP 协议越了解， 你就能越掌握Fiddler的使用方法。你越使用Fiddler，就越能帮助你了解HTTP协议。Fiddler无论对开发人员或者测试人员来说，都是非常有用的工具。<br>– 上述转载自<a href=\"https://www.cnblogs.com/zhaoyanjun/p/7068905.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">https://www.cnblogs.com/zhaoyanjun/p/7068905.html</a></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://s1.ax1x.com/2020/06/07/tRYtDP.jpg\" alt=\"1\"></p>\n<p>用我的话来说：<b>fiddle是专业的抓包工具，监控数据传输。</b></p>\n<h2 id=\"安装与使用\"><a href=\"#安装与使用\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"安装与使用\"></a>安装与使用</h2><ol>\n<li>导出fiddle的证书，导入浏览器中</li>\n<li>如下图配置，start测试即可使用</li>\n</ol>\n<p><img src=\"https://s1.ax1x.com/2020/06/07/tRtPqP.jpg\" alt=\"2\"></p>\n<p>tips：利用第二个浏览器，作为精确抓包测试的工具。</p>\n<h2 id=\"简易分析\"><a href=\"#简易分析\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"简易分析\"></a>简易分析</h2><ul>\n<li>获取不到的只能够通过抓包+分析获得，通常是由请求的第一个或第二个文件。</li>\n<li>翻页以后会有规律的参数，具体如下分析过程</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"测试用例\"><a href=\"#测试用例\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"测试用例\"></a>测试用例</h2><p><strong>python代码</strong>:</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight python\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br><span class=\"line\">19</span><br><span class=\"line\">20</span><br><span class=\"line\">21</span><br><span class=\"line\">22</span><br><span class=\"line\">23</span><br><span class=\"line\">24</span><br><span class=\"line\">25</span><br><span class=\"line\">26</span><br><span class=\"line\">27</span><br><span class=\"line\">28</span><br><span class=\"line\">29</span><br><span class=\"line\">30</span><br><span class=\"line\">31</span><br><span class=\"line\">32</span><br><span class=\"line\">33</span><br><span class=\"line\">34</span><br><span class=\"line\">35</span><br><span class=\"line\">36</span><br><span class=\"line\">37</span><br><span class=\"line\">38</span><br><span class=\"line\">39</span><br><span class=\"line\">40</span><br><span class=\"line\">41</span><br><span class=\"line\">42</span><br><span class=\"line\">43</span><br><span class=\"line\">44</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">import</span> urllib.request</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">import</span> random</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">import</span> re</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># 规律总结：发现变化参数</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">cid = <span class=\"number\">6636227627315213305</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">endid = <span class=\"number\">1582815116256</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># 安全一点</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">uapools = UAPOOL = [</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"string\">\"Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64; rv:60.0) Gecko/20100101 Firefox/60.0\"</span>,</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"string\">\"Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 6.1) AppleWebKit/536.5\"</span>,</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"string\">\"Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 6.1; WOW64; rv:48.0) Gecko/20100101 Firefox/48.0\"</span>,</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"string\">\"Mozilla/4.0 (compatible; MISE 7.0; Windows NT 5.1; Maxthon 2.0)\"</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">]</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\"><span class=\"keyword\">def</span> <span class=\"title\">UA</span><span class=\"params\">()</span>:</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    opener = urllib.request.build_opener()</span><br><span class=\"line\">    thisua = random.choice(uapools)</span><br><span class=\"line\">    ua = (<span class=\"string\">\"User-Agent\"</span>,thisua)</span><br><span class=\"line\">    opener.addheaders = [ua]</span><br><span class=\"line\">    urllib.request.install_opener(opener)</span><br><span class=\"line\">    </span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\"><span class=\"keyword\">def</span> <span class=\"title\">save</span><span class=\"params\">(filename, contents)</span>:</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">      fh = open(filename, <span class=\"string\">'w'</span>, encoding=<span class=\"string\">'utf-8'</span>)</span><br><span class=\"line\">      fh.write(contents)</span><br><span class=\"line\">      fh.close()</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">for</span> i <span class=\"keyword\">in</span> range(<span class=\"number\">0</span>,<span class=\"number\">100</span>):</span><br><span class=\"line\">    print(<span class=\"string\">\"第\"</span>+str(i+<span class=\"number\">1</span>)+<span class=\"string\">\"页\"</span>)</span><br><span class=\"line\">    url = <span class=\"string\">\"https://video.coral.qq.com/varticle/4825888381/comment/v2?callback=_varticle4825888381commentv2&amp;orinum=10&amp;oriorder=o&amp;pageflag=1&amp;cursor=\"</span>+str(cid)+<span class=\"string\">\"&amp;scorecursor=0&amp;orirepnum=2&amp;reporder=o&amp;reppageflag=1&amp;source=132&amp;_=\"</span>+str(endid+i)</span><br><span class=\"line\">    UA()</span><br><span class=\"line\">    data = urllib.request.urlopen(url).read().decode(<span class=\"string\">\"utf-8\"</span>,<span class=\"string\">\"ignore\"</span>)</span><br><span class=\"line\">    pat = <span class=\"string\">'\"content\":\"(.*?)\"'</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    comments = re.compile(pat,re.S).findall(data)</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">for</span> item <span class=\"keyword\">in</span> comments:</span><br><span class=\"line\">        string = str(eval(<span class=\"string\">'u\"'</span>+str(item)+<span class=\"string\">'\"'</span>))</span><br><span class=\"line\">        newdata =  string +<span class=\"string\">'\\n----\\n'</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        print(string)</span><br><span class=\"line\">        print(<span class=\"string\">'----'</span>)</span><br><span class=\"line\">        save(<span class=\"string\">'D:\\\\三生三世评论.txt'</span>, newdata)</span><br><span class=\"line\">    print(<span class=\"string\">'ok'</span>+str(i+<span class=\"number\">1</span>))</span><br><span class=\"line\">    pat2 = <span class=\"string\">'\"last\":\"(.*?)\"'</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    cid = re.compile(pat2,re.S).findall(data)[<span class=\"number\">0</span>]</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p><strong>输出结果</strong>：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br><span class=\"line\">19</span><br><span class=\"line\">20</span><br><span class=\"line\">21</span><br><span class=\"line\">22</span><br><span class=\"line\">23</span><br><span class=\"line\">24</span><br><span class=\"line\">25</span><br><span class=\"line\">26</span><br><span class=\"line\">27</span><br><span class=\"line\">28</span><br><span class=\"line\">29</span><br><span class=\"line\">30</span><br><span class=\"line\">31</span><br><span class=\"line\">32</span><br><span class=\"line\">33</span><br><span class=\"line\">34</span><br><span class=\"line\">35</span><br><span class=\"line\">36</span><br><span class=\"line\">37</span><br><span class=\"line\">38</span><br><span class=\"line\">39</span><br><span class=\"line\">40</span><br><span class=\"line\">41</span><br><span class=\"line\">42</span><br><span class=\"line\">43</span><br><span class=\"line\">44</span><br><span class=\"line\">45</span><br><span class=\"line\">46</span><br><span class=\"line\">47</span><br><span class=\"line\">48</span><br><span class=\"line\">49</span><br><span class=\"line\">50</span><br><span class=\"line\">51</span><br><span class=\"line\">52</span><br><span class=\"line\">53</span><br><span class=\"line\">54</span><br><span class=\"line\">55</span><br><span class=\"line\">56</span><br><span class=\"line\">57</span><br><span class=\"line\">58</span><br><span class=\"line\">59</span><br><span class=\"line\">60</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">第1页</span><br><span class=\"line\">两个憨憨讨论爱情也是绝了，小燕壮士这脑洞大破天啊，司命的剧本已经过时了，不如换小燕来写，相爱相杀虐恋情深还挺带感呢！</span><br><span class=\"line\">----</span><br><span class=\"line\">我总感觉司命也喜欢凤九?</span><br><span class=\"line\">----</span><br><span class=\"line\">本VIP表面波澜不惊，内心风起云涌想看点播，姐妹们给我点力量！</span><br><span class=\"line\">----</span><br><span class=\"line\">感觉这周的很精彩就来了#东华凤九甜度爆表#小凤九最可爱了</span><br><span class=\"line\">----</span><br><span class=\"line\">我最爱最吃他们两的颜值。迪丽热巴和东华帝君。好想上东华。他无欲无求只对凤九有吧。哈哈😃</span><br><span class=\"line\">----</span><br><span class=\"line\">妈耶，这也太好康了</span><br><span class=\"line\">----</span><br><span class=\"line\">会员就是爽啊！抑制不住的激动</span><br><span class=\"line\">----</span><br><span class=\"line\">姬衡配不上小燕魔</span><br><span class=\"line\">君。</span><br><span class=\"line\">----</span><br><span class=\"line\">外面有人😯</span><br><span class=\"line\">----</span><br><span class=\"line\">好奇怪为什么姬蘅会喜欢上帝君，之前不是喜欢那个女扮男装的谁谁吗？后面到凡间也没有喜欢王君,然后她记忆恢复之后就喜欢了，难道是帝君那时候让她去梵音古疗伤她要求给帝君侍寝慢慢就喜欢了？如果是这样的话她也太善变了吧,后面好像还耍心机之前也没见她这样</span><br><span class=\"line\">----</span><br><span class=\"line\">而且终于可以花钱提前看了</span><br><span class=\"line\">----</span><br><span class=\"line\">棒棒哒</span><br><span class=\"line\">----</span><br><span class=\"line\">好温暖的帝君，还给凤九端药。</span><br><span class=\"line\">----</span><br><span class=\"line\">好</span><br><span class=\"line\">----</span><br><span class=\"line\">是啊，会员可以超前点播到42集了，太激动了</span><br><span class=\"line\">----</span><br><span class=\"line\">我是会员，我怎么不能</span><br><span class=\"line\">----</span><br><span class=\"line\">相信我，这两集看完后如果你忍不住去点播了，你看到的，绝对不是你一个人，也许还有我哈哈哈哈哈哈</span><br><span class=\"line\">----</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">----</span><br><span class=\"line\">支持你上，😄</span><br><span class=\"line\">----</span><br><span class=\"line\">高伟光把帝君演的绝了</span><br><span class=\"line\">----</span><br><span class=\"line\">不用感觉他就是喜欢</span><br><span class=\"line\">----</span><br><span class=\"line\">我的小凤九你回头看看司命</span><br><span class=\"line\">----</span><br><span class=\"line\">之前就有心机，短兵图不是她改的 她却默认了</span><br><span class=\"line\">----</span><br><span class=\"line\">在凡间就喜欢了</span><br><span class=\"line\">----</span><br><span class=\"line\">很有同感，司命退位让贤吧！剧本都没有小燕魔君写的脑洞大，小燕魔君表情都可以做成表情包了</span><br><span class=\"line\">----</span><br><span class=\"line\">小燕真是傻的可爱，我都忍不住想过去劝他</span><br><span class=\"line\">----</span><br><span class=\"line\">放开小燕魔君，让我来</span><br><span class=\"line\">----</span><br><span class=\"line\">我也觉得</span><br><span class=\"line\">----</span><br><span class=\"line\">ok1</span><br><span class=\"line\">...</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>",
